YOUNG people will be able to find out more about what it takes to work for Scotland's largest health board. Health board to chat with job hopefuls YOUNG people will be able to find out more about what it takes to work for Scotland's largest health board.NHS Greater Glasgow and Clyde will be attending the Skills Scotland event at the SECC on October 29 and 30.Young people will be able to talk to NHSGGC recruitment advisors and job specialists in science and technology, administration and nursing. 